        public static final java.lang.String CLOUDGRAPH_COUNTER_NAME_TOT_GRAPH_ASSEMBLY_TIME
        MapReduce counter which stores the total time in milliseconds taken for graph assembly. Note: this time counter is summed across all tasks on all hosts so could exceed the total time taken for the job, as the tasks of course run in parallel.
